1083
01:09:19,688 --> 01:09:21,485
But he's a 4400.
He's our jurisdiction.

1084
01:09:21,657 --> 01:09:24,057
And someone at the Pentagon
signed an order overriding us.

1085
01:09:24,226 --> 01:09:25,887
Apparently,
they feel we lack experience

1086
01:09:26,061 --> 01:09:27,460
in high-pressure interrogation.

1087
01:09:27,663 --> 01:09:29,654
And who do you think put
that little bug in their ear?

1088
01:09:29,832 --> 01:09:32,767
I don't know if it was Ryland or not.
But we had our shot at Navarro.

1089
01:09:32,935 --> 01:09:34,095
Now, tomorrow is October 1 9th.

1090
01:09:34,270 --> 01:09:36,397
We are a day away
from an announced terrorist attack.

1091
01:09:36,572 --> 01:09:39,097
The NSA thinks
they can get him to talk.

1092
01:09:39,275 --> 01:09:42,574
- So where are they taking him?
- They didn't share that information.

1093
01:09:42,745 --> 01:09:45,543
This is so wrong.
This is the only place in the country

1094
01:09:45,714 --> 01:09:48,012
