into his car.

1101
01:10:20,282 --> 01:10:24,810
Oh, we're just gonna try another clinic,
but we will be away for a while.

1102
01:10:24,987 --> 01:10:26,921
- Do you want me to come with you?
- No.

1103
01:10:27,089 --> 01:10:29,080
No, it's all right. Thank you.

1104
01:10:29,625 --> 01:10:32,788
Now, if there's anything that you need,
you can talk to Shawn.

1105
01:10:32,962 --> 01:10:33,951
He's...

1106
01:10:34,129 --> 01:10:37,223
He'll be looking out for you, okay?

1107
01:10:39,435 --> 01:10:40,527
And...

1108
01:10:41,070 --> 01:10:43,470
I wanna give you this.

1109
01:10:45,808 --> 01:10:49,744
It's my wedding band.
I inherited it from my grandmother.

1110
01:10:50,446 --> 01:10:52,880
Her name was Lily too.

1111
01:10:55,551 --> 01:10:58,645
You used to love to play with it
when you were a little baby.

1112
01:10:59,521 --> 01:11:01,489
I remember.

1113
01:11:02,558 --> 01:11:06,255
- I used to like to bite on it.
- And my finger too.

1114
01:11:07,630 --> 01:11:08,756
You can wear it if you want.

1115
01:11:08,964 --> 01:11:12,627
I always knew
that I would give it to you one day.

1116
01:11:13,669 --> 01:11:18,333
It doesn't fit me anymore,
and I'd hate to lose it.

1117
01:11:19,908 --> 01:11:21,967
I'll keep it safe for you.

1118
01:11:23,812 --> 01:11:25,439
I know you will.

1119
01:11:27,616 --> 01:11:30,847
I'm sorry I have to leave so soon.

1120
01:11:31,387 --> 01:11:33,480
I wish we had more time together.

1121
01:11:34,056 --> 01:11:36,024
Well, when do you think
you'll be back?

1122
01:11:36,191 --> 01:11:37,317
It's hard to say.

1123
01:11:38,594 --> 01:11:40,619
Goodbye, lsabelle.

1124
01:11:48,637 --> 01:11:50,332
Bye.

1125
01:12:16,665 --> 01:12:19,031
Thank you very much.
I'll take her from here.

1126
01:12:19,201 --> 01:12:20,828
Thank you.

1127
01:12:21,603 --> 01:12:22,831
Okay,

1128
01:12:23,405 --> 01:12:26,374
you told her we were going over
to the hospital?

1129
01:12:27,743 --> 01:12:31,235
- How'd it go over?
- Oh, fine.

1130
01:12:31,413 --> 01:12:34,644
I had it easy. I got to lie.

1131
01:12:39,588 --> 01:12:42,648
You're the one
who has to tell her the truth.

1132
01:13:19,928 --> 01:13:21,953
What's going on?

1133
01:13:22,264 --> 01:13:24,198
What's happening?

1134
01:13:40,215 --> 01:13:41,204
We'll get him.

1135
01:13:41,383 --> 01:13:43,647
Funny, that's the exact same thing
Navarro said about you.

1136
01:13:43,819 --> 01:13:44,979
So far, he's wrong.

1137
01:13:45,154 --> 01:13:47,054
He never should've been moved
in the first place.

1138
01:13:47,222 --> 01:13:49,053
- There was no reason.
- There was every reason.

1139
01:13:49,224 --> 01:13:51,692
You're too soft, Tom.
I don't know what's happened to you.

1140
01:13:51,860 --> 01:13:53,589
No, I had him, Dennis! You lost him.

1141
01:13:55,130 --> 01:13:56,256
Sunset's in four hours.

1142
01:13:56,432 --> 01:13:58,400
At this point, we can't even say
with 1 00% certainty

1143
01:13:58,567 --> 01:14:00,159
