I feel a little naked standing out here.

1154
01:14:45,981 --> 01:14:47,710
Thanks.

1155
01:14:48,984 --> 01:14:51,578
Listen,
if there's ever anything you need--

1156
01:14:57,392 --> 01:14:59,383
You sold us--

1157
01:15:05,701 --> 01:15:06,725
Get in there, get in there.

1158
01:15:11,573 --> 01:15:14,167
- You okay?
- Yeah, I'm fine.

1159
01:15:14,877 --> 01:15:16,970
I don't guess we'll be seeing her
in court anytime soon.

1160
01:15:17,145 --> 01:15:19,306
No, you did the right thing
by calling us, Shawn.

1161
01:15:19,481 --> 01:15:20,607
Seriously.

1162
01:15:21,049 --> 01:15:22,949
You're a hero.

1163
01:15:45,841 --> 01:15:47,809
One minute to go.

1164
01:15:49,111 --> 01:15:52,740
Just tell me one thing.
Are we as prepared as we can be?

1165
01:15:52,915 --> 01:15:54,883
The entire country's
on level-red terror alert.

1166
01:15:55,050 --> 01:15:57,883
All commercial air traffic
has been suspended for the day.

1167
01:15:58,053 --> 01:16:01,022
The National Guard
has been deployed to likely targets.

1168
01:16:01,323 --> 01:16:03,553
"Likely targets." Kind of a broad term.

1169
01:16:03,725 --> 01:16:05,556
I wish T.J. could've narrowed
that down for us.

1170
01:16:05,727 --> 01:16:09,686
Well, me too. But we have to keep her
sedated to inhibit her ability.

1171
01:16:09,865 --> 01:16:13,323
