into a war zone once.

1172
01:16:14,336 --> 01:16:16,429
So now we wait.

1173
01:16:17,139 --> 01:16:20,802
Anyone else feel like they're staring
at a doomsday clock?

1174
01:16:33,555 --> 01:16:35,250
Well, that's it.

1175
01:16:35,424 --> 01:16:37,517
October 1 9th.

1176
01:16:39,127 --> 01:16:41,618
Looks like the world's still here.

1177
01:16:41,830 --> 01:16:44,025
For the moment, anyway.

1178
01:17:01,149 --> 01:17:03,083
Oh, my God!

1179
01:17:06,088 --> 01:17:09,182
- What? What happened?
- It's the Nova Group.

1180
01:17:09,358 --> 01:17:11,121
Certainly, "miracle"
is an imprecise term,

1181
01:17:11,293 --> 01:17:13,261
but I'm not sure hoW else
to describe it,

1182
