To repeat:

1183
01:17:14,596 --> 01:17:17,224
I'm broadcasting live from
the Nubian Desert, north of Khartoum,

1184
01:17:17,399 --> 01:17:20,891
Where overnight,
a thousand-acre patch of barren sand

1185
01:17:21,069 --> 01:17:24,300
