is real and edible,

1188
01:17:30,479 --> 01:17:32,572
There hasn't been food growing
in that part of the world

1189
01:17:32,748 --> 01:17:34,443
since before the birth of Christ.

1190
01:17:34,650 --> 01:17:36,811
They make us all terrified,

1191
01:17:36,985 --> 01:17:40,148
